import { Button, Col, Form, Row } from "react-bootstrap";
import React from "react";



function ProfileDetails() {
  return (
    <Form className="p-2 p-t-3 p-md-3 p-xl-5 w-m-50">
      <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="Name">
        <Form.Label 
          column 
          className="sr-only"
        >
          FirstName
        </Form.Label>
        <Col>
          <Form.Control
            name="firstName"
            type="text"
            placeholder="First Name"
            className="m-0 p-1"
          />
        </Col>
        <Form.Label 
          column 
          className="sr-only"
        >
          LastName
        </Form.Label>
        <Col>
          <Form.Control 
            type="text" 
            placeholder="Last Name" 
            className="m-0" 
          />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>

      <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="title">
        <Form.Label column className="sr-only">
          Title
        </Form.Label>
        <Col>
          <Form.Control 
            type="text" 
            placeholder="Title" 
            className="m-0" 
          />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>

      <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="company">
        <Form.Label column className="sr-only">
          Company
        </Form.Label>
        <Col>
          <Form.Control 
            className="m-0" 
            placeholder="Company" 
            type="text" 
            />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>

      <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="location">
        <Form.Label column className="sr-only">
          City
        </Form.Label>
        <Col>
          <Form.Control 
            className="m-0" 
            placeholder="City" 
            type="text" 
          />
        </Col>
        <Form.Label column className="sr-only">
          Country
        </Form.Label>
        <Col>
          <Form.Control 
            type="text" 
            placeholder="Country" 
            className="m-0" 
          />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>

      <Button type="submit">Save</Button>
    </Form>
  );
}

export default ProfileDetails;
